<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ xū yào yé sū zài wǒ de shēng mìng zhōng, wǒ xū yào yé sū zài wǒ de shēng mìng zhōng.
 wǒ xū yào yé sū zài wǒ de shēng mìng zhōng, wǒ xū yào yé sū zài wǒ de shēng mìng zhōng.
 yīn wèi rén shēng zhī lù, qí qū yòu màn zhǎng. yīn wèi lù tú shàng cháng cháng huì yǒu fēng làng.
 yīn wèi rén shēng chù chù dōu yǒu hěn duō de xiàn jǐng, wéi yǒu yé sū cái shì wǒ shēng mìng de bǎo zhàng.
 wǒ xū yào yé sū zài wǒ de shēng mìng zhōng, wǒ zhēn xū yào yé sū zài wǒ de shēng mìng zhōng.
 yé sū a nǐ lái ba, zài wǒ de shēng mìng zhōng. yǒng hé nǐ zài yī qǐ, gòng tóng dù shí guāng.</lyrics>
